Speaker 2: I don't think so, but let me give you another card.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: Yeah, whenever you're ready, feel free to give me the card number.

Speaker 1: Had to get up from my sitting position.

Speaker 2: Okay.

Speaker 1: The expiration is 9-28.

Speaker 1: 5-28.

Speaker 1: Let me try this out now.

Speaker 2: All right, you're all set.
